  "name": "Speak With Dead",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This spell allows the caster to ask several questions of a corpse. The corpse can answer questions that the creature knew in life. It will answer in its own language. Answers are usually brief, cryptic or repetitive. If the alignment of the caster is opposed to that of the corpse, it resists answering and the caster must make a check as if against spell resistance of 12. Only one <em>speak with dead</em> spell per week can be used on a corpse.</p>",
